Esther Rolle

Dead

Born: 11/8/1920 in Pompano Beach, Florida, USA

Died: 11/17/1998

Age: 78

Cause of death: complications from diabetes

Noted For: actress; "Maude" (Florida Evans, 1972-74), "Good Times" (Florida Evans, 1974-79).
